{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"诸位好！来看表演吗？","tone":"调侃","chapter":36,"line_start":7,"line_end":7},{"speaker":"char_shang_ming","speaker_name":"尚明","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"卑鄙小人。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":36,"line_start":9,"line_end":9},{"speaker":"char_shan_wan_jing","speaker_name":"单琬晶","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"还以为你们给人掳走了。现在看到你们生龙活虎，才知你们与宇文成都同流合污来打我们主意，今趟就叫天网恢恢，疏而不漏。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":36,"line_start":11,"line_end":15},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shan_wan_jing","text":"公主切勿误会，我们不但不认识宇文成都，他宇文阀还是我们的大仇人呢。","tone":"焦急","chapter":36,"line_start":17,"line_end":19},{"speaker":"char_shang_bang","speaker_name":"尚邦","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"难得夫人那么看得起你们，可你们却偏要伤她的心；无论你两个是否认识宇文成都，和他是甚么关系，但你们要去偷东西，却是不移的事实。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":36,"line_start":21,"line_end":23},{"speaker":"char_shang_kui_yi","speaker_name":"尚奎义","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"究竟是谁指使你们？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":36,"line_start":25,"line_end":25},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_shang_kui_yi","text":"有话好说，怎会有人指使我们呢？","tone":"陪笑","chapter":36,"line_start":27,"line_end":27},{"speaker":"char_shan_wan_jing","speaker_name":"单琬晶","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"若不是有人指点，你又怎知会有这么一本账簿呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":36,"line_start":33,"line_end":35},{"speaker":"char_shang_ming","speaker_name":"尚明","listener":null,"text":"与这种小脚色说话只是浪费时间，押他们出去。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":36,"line_start":37,"line_end":37},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_shan_wan_jing","text":"假若你们动手，本高手立即大叫救命，所以动手前最好三思。","tone":"调侃","chapter":36,"line_start":41,"line_end":43},{"speaker":"char_shen_wu_shuang","speaker_name":"沈无双","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"小狗想逃吗？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":36,"line_start":103,"line_end":105}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_kou_zhong","name":"寇仲","alias":["少帅","仲少"],"identity":"扬州双龙之一