{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shen_wu_shuang","speaker_name":"沈无双","listener":"char_shan_wan_jing","text":"原来另有同党，怪不得这么威风。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":36,"line_start":111,"line_end":113},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_shen_wu_shuang","text":"无双妹误会了。他们只是要求我们到门外去，好研究一下拳脚功夫吧。","tone":"调侃","chapter":36,"line_start":115,"line_end":117},{"speaker":"char_shen_wu_shuang","speaker_name":"沈无双","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"谁是你的无双妹？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":36,"line_start":119,"line_end":119},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shen_wu_shuang","text":"自己人不要那么吵好吗？我们只是来作客，不是来和人吵架动手的。","tone":"无奈","chapter":36,"line_start":121,"line_end":123},{"speaker":"char_shan_wan_jing","speaker_name":"单琬晶","listener":"char_shen_wu_shuang","text":"快让路！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":36,"line_start":125,"line_end":125},{"speaker":"char_shen_wu_shuang","speaker_name":"沈无双","listener":"char_shan_wan_jing","text":"你给我滚才对，让我整治了这两只小狗，才和你们算账。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":36,"line_start":127,"line_end":129},{"speaker":"char_shang_ming","speaker_name":"尚明","listener":"char_shen_wu_shuang","text":"臭丫头凭甚么质格来和我们算帐。","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":36,"line_start":131,"line_end":131},{"speaker":"char_meng_chang","speaker_name":"孟昌","listener":"char_shang_ming","text":"好胆！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":36,"line_start":133,"line_end":133},{"speaker":"char_meng_ran","speaker_name":"孟然","listener":"char_shang_ming","text":"好胆！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":36,"line_start":133,"line_end":133},{"speaker":"char_shen_nai_tang","speaker_name":"沈乃堂","listener":null,"text":"你们干甚么？知否这是甚么地方？","tone":"严肃","chapter":36,"line_start":137,"line_end":137},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_shen_nai_tang","text":"不关我们兄弟的事，是他们闹起来的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":36,"line_start":145,"line_end":147},{"speaker":"char_shan_wan_jing","speaker_name":"单琬晶","listener":"char_wang_tong","text":"惊动通老了。哈！没事哩。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":36,"line_start