{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":309,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lan_yi_da_han","speaker_name":"蓝衣大汉","listener":null,"text":"谁敢来撒野！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":36,"line_start":203,"line_end":205},{"speaker":"char_ou_yang_xi_yi","speaker_name":"欧阳希夷","listener":"char_ba_feng_han","text":"好！英雄出少年，来人与突厥的毕玄究竟是何关系？","tone":"豪迈","chapter":36,"line_start":225,"line_end":227},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":"char_ou_yang_xi_yi","text":"原来是'黄山逸民'欧阳希夷，难怪眼力如此高明，不过在下非但与毕玄毫无关系，还是他欲得之而甘心的人。","tone":"平静","chapter":36,"line_start":233,"line_end":235},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"那美人儿有点像娘。","tone":"低语","chapter":36,"line_start":243,"line_end":243},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"这小鬼看来厉害得很，否则眼神不会那么亮如电闪。","tone":"低语","chapter":36,"line_start":247,"line_end":247},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"人群中某人","listener":"char_ba_feng_han","text":"小鬼凭甚么资格连毕玄都要着紧你的小命呢？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":36,"line_start":251,"line_end":253},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"这种事看来没有解释的必要吧！","tone":"淡然","chapter":36,"line_start":255,"line_end":257},{"speaker":"char_wang_tong","speaker_name":"王通","listener":"char_ba_feng_han","text":"阁下刚进门便伤人，王某虽不好舞刀弄棍，但仍不得不被迫出手，给我报上名来！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":36,"line_start":259,"line_end":261},{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":"char_chen_yuan_zhi","text":"有王老和欧阳老作主，陈当家请回吧。","tone":"严肃","chapter":36,"line_start":265,"line_end":267},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":"char_bai_yi_nv_zi","text":"在下跋锋寒，今趟与这位小姐结伴而来，是","tone":"陈述","chapter":36,"line_start":279,"line_end":279},{"speaker":"char_bai_yi_nv_zi","speaker_name":"白衣美女","listener":"char_ba_feng_han","text":"你还你，我还我，谁是你的伴儿。哼，是害怕了吗？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":36,"line_start":281,"line_end":283},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"这小鬼卖相倒不俗，喂！溜吧！